    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 295,
      "versionNonce": 2063965475,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "MQsR3amwAoWT2dqXXMbzd",
      "x": 1249.1326367721476,
      "y": 262.9281445481485,
      "width": 276.8206787109375,
      "height": 215.9127703229241,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2055030787,
      "text": "Recursive quadrant division\nO(log n) queries\nIn-memory only\n\nHow it works\n- Recursively divides the world map into 4 quadrants\n- Each node has 4 children (NW, NE, SW, SE)\n- Leaf nodes store nearby entities\n\nProblems\n- Assumes uniform data distribution (not true in reality)\n- Highly unbalanced trees in dense areas (cities)\n- Expensive traversal to find nearby results\n- Hard to update when new locations are added\n- Must be stored in memory, not a database\n\nVerdict\n❌ Avoid in real systems and interviews",
      "fontSize": 9.896001973134021,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "index": "aL",
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1766904827665,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Recursive quadrant division\nO(log n) queries\nIn-memory only\n\nHow it works\n- Recursively divides the world map into 4 quadrants\n- Each node has 4 children (NW, NE, SW, SE)\n- Leaf nodes store nearby entities\n\nProblems\n- Assumes uniform data distribution (not true in reality)\n- Highly unbalanced trees in dense areas (cities)\n- Expensive traversal to find nearby results\n- Hard to update when new locations are added\n- Must be stored in memory, not a database\n\nVerdict\n❌ Avoid in real systems and interviews",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2121212121212122
    },
