      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1189489091,
      "text": "How it works\n- Store location as a spatial data type\n- Use built-in spatial queries like ST_DWithin\n\nPros\n- Very simple to implement\n- Accurate distance calculations\n- No custom indexing logic needed\n\nCons\n- Slower at very large scale\n- Best for moderate datasets\n\nVerdict\n\n✅ Great for backend-heavy systems with SQL",
      "fontSize": 9.908970530777529,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "index": "aR",
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1766904861699,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How it works\n- Store location as a spatial data type\n- Use built-in spatial queries like ST_DWithin\n\nPros\n- Very simple to implement\n- Accurate distance calculations\n- No custom indexing logic needed\n\nCons\n- Slower at very large scale\n- Best for moderate datasets\n\nVerdict\n\n✅ Great for backend-heavy systems with SQL",
