      "seed": 419904675,
      "text": "How it works\n- Native geo-distance queries\n- Supports text + location search together\n\nPros\n- Best for text + location queries\n- Highly scalable\n- Plug-and-play\n\nCons\n- Extra infrastructure cost\n- Eventual consistency\n\nVerdict\n✅ Best for search-heavy applications",
