      "updated": 1767583108676,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "| Use Case                          | Best Choice                  |\n| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |\n| Nearby drivers / restaurants only | **Geohash**                  |\n| SQL-centric backend               | **PostgreSQL + PostGIS**     |\n| Text + location search            | **Elasticsearch**            |\n| Academic explanation only         | Quad Tree (but don’t use it) |\n",
      "fontSize": 11.932628053431072,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "| Use Case                          | Best Choice                  |\n| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |\n| Nearby drivers / restaurants only | **Geohash**                  |\n| SQL-centric backend               | **PostgreSQL + PostGIS**     |\n| Text + location search            | **Elasticsearch**            |\n| Academic explanation only         | Quad Tree (but don’t use it) |\n",
